00:08:18.190 --> 00:08:19.190
nurses.

00:08:19.190 --> 00:08:24.860
Making the increase in nurses seem astronomically
higher between 2010 and 2011, when in fact

00:08:24.860 --> 00:08:28.229
there was only a 7% increase.

00:08:28.229 --> 00:08:33.810
Another way that information is often misleadingly
visualised is through false correlations.

00:08:33.810 --> 00:08:38.669
This graph humorously suggests that there
is a positive correlation between ice creams

00:08:38.669 --> 00:08:41.079
sales and murders.

00:08:41.079 --> 00:08:45.829
But of course, correlation doesn’t imply
causation.

00:08:45.829 --> 00:08:50.780
Just because I usually take tea around the
same time that the pope holds morning mass,

00:08:50.780 --> 00:08:56.310
it doesn’t mean that I am in any way persuaded
