00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:11.800
Why does it matter if headlines are misleading?

00:12:11.800 --> 00:12:17.260
Because multiple studies concur that a headline’s
bias hugely affects the way the rest of the

00:12:17.260 --> 00:12:21.559
article is read and interpreted.

00:12:21.559 --> 00:12:26.620
Headlines provide us with the setup for the
story we are about to read and no matter if

00:12:26.620 --> 00:12:31.819
