00:12:51.290 --> 00:12:55.959
The wording of the headline also dictates
what we remember most from the news story

00:12:55.959 --> 00:12:59.759
and how we will report it to our friends.

00:12:59.759 --> 00:13:04.870
That’s assuming the person ever reads the
article.

00:13:04.870 --> 00:13:11.240
