00:15:57.170 --> 00:16:02.170
Other linguistic tricks are commonly used
by journalists when interviewing an adversary.

00:16:02.170 --> 00:16:06.699
I would love to show you example clips of
the following techniques in use but I’m

00:16:06.699 --> 00:16:12.500
