the UK they could not be fined.

00:20:23.870 --> 00:20:30.700
News is the mechanism by which public opinions
are formed and ideologies are built, it is

00:20:30.700 --> 00:20:37.360
therefore imperative that when we see wild
claims and incendiary headlines that we choose

00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:43.029
to dig a little deeper, consult other sources
and build one’s own balanced opinion on

00:20:43.029 --> 00:20:50.290
the matter instead of blindly copying that
of a single biased journalist.

00:20:50.290 --> 00:20:55.279
Especially in a world where we have misleading
headlines such as this “Girls’ school

00:20:55.279 --> 00:20:57.620
still offering ‘something special’ - head”.

00:20:57.620 --> 00:20:59.230
Thanks for watching.

